name: Green Trees Wallet
description:
This handmade cotton tri-fold wallet has a serene trees pattern. The wallet has a cash pocket and three credit cards slots with additional inside slots. Includes clear vinyl slot for an ID card. Pockets lined with a thin white waterproof nylon creating a thin but sturdy wallet. Held together with durable forest green nylon binding tape. It measures 9.5" long x 4" tall. Spray coated with a protective layer to preserve its new look.

Hand wash/air dry.

Note: Each wallet will be a bit different due to the repeating nature of the fabric.
